#526  Batman decides to spend a day stopping every crime in Gotham City--but can the Dark Knight handle it all or will overexertion take too much of a toll? 

#527  Two-Face has a rival. His name is Schism and he has literally two brains. With both villains at large, the threat to Gotham--and the Dark Knight--is redoubled. Or rather, quadrupled. 

#528  Batman must stop a rampage of death when Two-Face's search for an old enemy leads to a disturbing encounter at the circus. 

#529  "Contagion" part 6, continued from AZRAEL (1995-2003) #15. Robin, Nightwing and the Huntress try to suppress rioters as panic over the Clench virus spreads through Gotham City. Meanwhile, Batman's search for a cure leads him to Arkham Asylum! Continued in BATMAN: SHADOW OF THE BAT #49.
